@startuml Architecture
title Гексагональная архитектура: Expense Service ("Про рубли")
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

package "Infrastructure Layer" {
    [REST API Controller] as API
    [InMemory Expense Repository] as RepoAdapter
    [Push Notification Adapter] as PushAdapter
}

package "Application Layer" {
    portin "AddExpenseUseCase\nGetExpenseUseCase" as InPorts
    portout "ExpenseRepository\nNotificationService" as OutPorts
    [Expense Service] as AppService
}

package "Domain Layer" {
    [Expense Entity] as Expense
    [Category Entity] as Category
}

' Зависимости: Инфраструктура зависит от Application
API --> InPorts : Использует (вызов)
RepoAdapter -.-> OutPorts : Реализует
PushAdapter -.-> OutPorts : Реализует

' Зависимости: Application зависит от Domain
AppService ..|> InPorts : Реализует
AppService --> OutPorts : Вызывает
AppService --> Expense : Использует
AppService --> Category : Использует

' Правило зависимостей (Dependency Rule)
note bottom of "Domain Layer"
  Domain ничего не знает
  о внешних слоях!
end note
@enduml